⚠️  SECURITY DISCLAIMER — PLEASE READ BEFORE USE ⚠️

THIS SOFTWARE HANDLES GITHUB PERSONAL ACCESS TOKENS (PATs) ENTERED DIRECTLY
BY THE USER IN THE BROWSER.

- Your token is stored in your browser's `localStorage` and is transmitted
  directly to `api.github.com` and `models.github.com` as a Bearer token on
  every API request made while the app is running.

- THIS APPLICATION WAS VIBE-CODED AND HAS NOT UNDERGONE A FORMAL SECURITY
  AUDIT.  No guarantees are made about the security, correctness, or
  reliability of the code.

- You use this application ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN RISK.  The authors accept NO
  responsibility for any loss, data breach, account compromise, or other harm
  that may result from using this software or from entering your GitHub token
  into it.

- NEVER enter tokens with write or admin scopes unless you fully understand
  the implications and trust the code you are running.

- Always review the source code yourself before entering any credentials.

By using this software you acknowledge that you have read this disclaimer and
accept all associated risks.
